{"tid":1182940,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"6月9上街無撚用？","createTime":"2019-06-02T14:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T06:53:44.000Z","uid":247972,"like":10,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"90155a3b3b2ccc5c02da7aeea9b555faf49f148a","tid":1182940,"uid":247972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"遊行已經係舊時代既抗爭手段<br />\n又老土又唔夠宣染力<br />\n要令訊息傳遍社會每一角落<br />\n除左靠遊行 要靠埋social media（社交媒體）<br />\n<br />\n不過思想封建既連登仔根本唔識尼d野<br />\n小弟(ig followers 2k+)就開左兩個post教大家學識新世代社交<br />\n想話教大家一齊做個proficient socialist<br />\n但反應似乎不太好 似乎我既付出只感化到幾個人<br />\n但用得連登就要愛屋及鳥<br />\n<br />\n今個post就把握69遊行 <br />\n教大家善用social media to strengthen 大家既impact（影響）<br />\n我稱之為 media synchronised socialism-driven protest<br />\n<br />\n有d咩可以加強69protest 既effectiveness 呢？<br />\n最主要方法就係參與既同時po ig!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n有幾項要注意！<br />\n<br />\n1. 要影到人群 (最好用黑白相po）咁做可以令人感受到一種落莫<br />\n2. 正如上個post 有講，一定要有hashtag!!!!! <br />\n但要用d有士氣既字眼 去令人有認同既感覺 <br />\n例如#stronger （更強大）<br />\n#together（一起）<br />\n #endgame （尼個唔洗翻譯）<br />\n#lastfightingchance（最後抗爭機會）<br />\n<br />\n咁樣兩個功效配合起尼，就會令人感到有曙光<br />\n因為係一個pessimistic（悲歡）atmosphere（氣氛）中，都有奮鬥既意識.<br />\n<br />\n最後 caption 可以唔洗打太多<br />\n太多字就會有d over，個情感會好excessive （過量）, 會令人好overwhelming<br />\n<br />\n實際例子有人問我再評價下<br />\n<br />\n擺返早兩個post<br />\n第一個教大家寫ig bio (<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cHmqfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cHmqfS</a>)<br />\n第二個教大家出ig post (<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cHuJnS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cHuJnS</a>)<br />\n<br />\n記住！新時代要用新時代既方法，即social media<br />\n要leverage media既力量！"},{"pid":"0b62d4bb2b5587cb46d1d6f06cfdc43c0899bbff","tid":1182940,"uid":247972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d54fa8a6f6bda76e6a2b802f5c9429da4245f0","tid":1182940,"uid":55614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T